{"tid":435161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最近坐地鐵見到支付寶廣告嚇一跳, 細心睇完得啖笑","createTime":"2017-10-14T04:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T16:24:44.000Z","uid":78620,"like":323,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"310fc4df08badfed6db9f293b8643683b9cf7d1c","tid":435161,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"早2日係地鐵見到勁大型支付寶廣告, 貼到成個車廂都係, 諗緊係咪共產黨又打到黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/14/122250_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F14%2F122250_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c6981fd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/14/121751_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F14%2F121751_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d0daec83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買野85折, 岩哂貪小便宜嘅香港人啦, 但係再睇真d句細字......<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/14/121857_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F14%2F121857_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=963efe3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n得大陸戶口有優惠, 早排支付寶先鎖左大陸戶口要有大陸身份證先用得, 想點? 得啖笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3e009c5ab194fc56142f73cbf1ef21225e75a9","tid":435161,"uid":63154,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:28:50.000Z","msg":"即係想你香港人搬錢過深圳開戶口"}